Metrorail warned of "major delays" in an advisory to commuters stating: "Residual damage by a delivery truck affects signal equipment".A train shuttle is operating from Retreat to Fish Hoek while a bus and train shuttle is running between Fish Hoek and Simon's Town.Anticipated delays of between 50 to 60 plus minutes are expected Metrorail said.There are also some trains cancelled "due to sets out of service". These are on the Retreat to Cape Town line and between Fish Hoek and Cape Town.